tafsir[10]{c,v,t}:
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah yaГұГұani Й“ernde mun fii lislaamu, o feewi e mun, hara himo e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi makko, wa'ata wa yoora Й“enrdeejo e jantagol Allah? ЖҒe fotataa fes. Tawde ko feewuЙ“e Й“en, daЙ—ata, yoora Й“erЙ—e'en e jantagol Allah .ЖҒen wonii e majjere Й“anngunde."
  39,23,"Allah jppinii e NulaaЙ—o Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his) Alqur'aana, Й“urnde moЖҙЖҙude yewtere. O waЙ—i nden nanndude ka goonga, e ka moЖҙЖҙugol, e ka yuЙ“Й“ondirgol e waasde luutondirde. Fillayeeji e Гұaawooje hino Й—uuЙ—i e mayre, kaГұum e fodooje e kammbaa, e sifaaji yimЙ“e goonga, e yimЙ“e meere Й“en ekn. Guri Й“en hulooЙ“e Joomi mun, hino riЙ“ira sabu nanugol kammbaaji ko woni e mayre, refti guri e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e deeЖҙira jantagol Innde Allah, tuma Й“e nani jortagol e welo-welo ko woni e mayre. Koo ko jantaa e ko Alqur'aana battinta, ko peewal Allah, ngal O fewnirta mo O muuyani, O hoyna mo Mo O muuyani. Kala non mo Allah fewnaali, haray fewnoowo mo alaa."
  39,24,"Kere on mo Allah fewni aduna, O naadoya mo Aljanna laakara, on fotay wa yedduЙ—o maayi e keeferaaku on, naatoyoowo Yiite, tonnge juuЙ—e e koyЙ—e, mo tawata waawoytaa daЙ—irde Yiite ngen, si wanaa tun o fewtinira nge yeeso makko ngon? TooГұuЙ“e Й“en feliree wi'aneede ontuma: meeЙ—en non hannde, kon ko wonunoЙ—on faggitorde geddi e keeferaaku. Ko njoЙ“di mon ndin nii."
  39,25,"Mofte adinooЙ“e Й“ee sirkooЙ“e, kadi fennuno NulaaЙ“e mun, lepte Й—en ardirani Й“e juhal, fewndo ka Й“e so'aa-anndude, sakko Й“e hebiloranaЙ—e tuubugol."
  39,26,"Allah meeЙ—iriЙ“e sabu Й—um, lepte koyeera, e jaasere, e wirtere ka ngurrndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte laakara Й—en habbitiiЙ—e Й“e, Й“uri mawnude e tiiЙ—e, si tawno hiЙ“e anndunoo."
  39,27,"GomЙ—ii Men piyanii yimЙ“e Й“en, e ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo o his) noone kala e mise moЖҙЖҙere e bone, goonga e meere, gomЙ—inal e keeferaaku, ekn. ЖҠum fow, ko jortagol nde Й“e waajitora, Й“e huutora goonga kan, Й“e sela meere nden."
  39,28,"Men waЙ—i nde Alqur'aanaare, janngeteende e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e ooГұaare maa jiЙ“i-liЙ“i, jortagol no Й“e hulira Allah, jokkugol yamiraaЙ—i Makko, woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko."
  39,29,"Allah waЙ—ii misal hakkunde sirkoowo e wootinЙ—inoowo, woni gorko mo lurruЙ“e hawti : si o weltinii woЙ—Й“e Й“en, Й“eya Й“en monoo, o wona e jiЙ“i-liЙ“i. Oya gorko, ko laaЙ“anЙ—o gorko goo, kanko tun, himo anndi ko deeЖҙinta oya, e ko wallinta mo Й“ernde. ЖҒen worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, Й“e fotataa e misal. Yettoore woodanii Allah. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa. Ko waЙ—i si Й“e kafida e Allah, goЙ—Й—um goo."
  39,30,"Pelelt, an NulaaЙ—o, ko a maayoowo, kamЙ“e kadi ko Й“e maayooЙ“e, feere mun alaa."
  39,31,"Refti onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, Г‘alnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon yeddondiroyton, e ko pooЙ—ondiraynoЙ—on fii mun, goonguЙ—o on seerta e meerenteejo on."
